ate     = {{Start date|2001|1|18}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 16\n| Title               = Conflict and Decisions\n| AltTitle            = Katt\u014d to Ketsui to\n| NativeTitle         = \u845b\u85e4\u3068\u6c7a\u610f\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|1|25}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 17\n| Title               = Decisions and the Past\n| AltTitle            = Ketsui to Kako to\n| NativeTitle         = \u6c7a\u610f\u3068\u904e\u53bb\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|2|1}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 18\n| Title               = The Past and Crimes\n| AltTitle            = Kako to Daizai to\n| NativeTitle         = \u904e\u53bb\u3068\u5927\u7f6a\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|2|8}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 19\n| Title               = Crimes and Punishments\n| AltTitle            = Daizai to Imashime to\n| NativeTitle         = \u5927\u7f6a\u3068\u6212\u3081\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|2|15}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 20\n| Title               = Punishments and Awakening\n| AltTitle            = Imashime to Kakusei to\n| NativeTitle         = \u6212\u3081\u3068\u899a\u9192\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|2|22}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 21\n| Title               = Awakening and Truth\n| AltTitle            = Kakusei to Shinjitsu to\n| NativeTitle         = \u899a\u9192\u3068\u771f\u5b9f\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|3|1}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 22\n| Title               = Truth and Destruction\n| AltTitle            = Shinjitsu to Hametsu to\n| NativeTitle         = \u771f\u5b9f\u3068\u7834\u6ec5\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|3|8}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 23\n| Title               = Destruction and Courage\n| AltTitle            = Hametsu to Y\u016bki to\n| NativeTitle         = \u7834\u6ec5\u3068\u52c7\u6c17\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|3|15}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 24\n| Title               = Courage and Love\n| AltTitle            = Y\u016bki to Ai to\n| NativeTitle         = \u52c7\u6c17\u3068\u611b\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|3|22}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = 25\n| Title               = Love and Rebirth\n| AltTitle            = Ai to Saisei to\n| NativeTitle         = \u611b\u3068\u518d\u751f\u3068\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2001|3|29}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber       = OVA\n| Title               = Alone and By Myself\n| AltTitle            = Kodoku to Kodoku\n| NativeTitle         = \u5b64\u72ec\u3068\u5b64\u72ec\n| NativeTitleLangCode = ja \n| OriginalAirDate     = {{Start date|2002|2|21}}\n| ShortSummary        = \n}}\n}}\n\n== Music ==\n\n===''OP Single - Silent Wind''===\n{{Infobox song\n| name     = Argento Soma - Silent Wind\n| cover    =\n| alt      =\n| type     = song\n| artist   = [[Eri Sugai]]\n| album    =\n| released = Nov 22, 2000\n| format   =\n| recorded =\n| studio   =\n| venue    =\n| genre    = [[Anime]]\n| length   =\n| label    = [[Victor Entertainment]]\n| composer = [[Katsuhisa Hattori]]\n| lyricist = [[Kitagawa Keiko]]\n| producer =\n}}\nThe single album to the opening song\n\n{{tracklist\n|collapsed =No\n|headline =Track Listing\n|title1  =Silent Wind\n|length1 